arChildNodes.szComment:
EXT. HAWEZAR- SERPENT ALTAR
Neyrelle and Lorath are surrounded by smoke from the incense. We hear them inhale deeply.

Lorath starts to sit by the altar. Neyrelle and the Player do the same.
          FADE OUT
          FADE IN
Incense is everywhere. Lorath, Neyrelle, and the Player have fallen asleep (due to the incense smoke).
A SHADOWY FORM moves in the jungle around them. It’s the SERPENT. HUGE AND UNSETTLING.
Lorath’s eyes open. He’s half awake, in a twilight state.
In the distance, through smoke and shadow, he sees the snake.
His heavy eyelids shut, lulled back to sleep by the incense.

The snake slithers off into the jungle.
          FADE OUT
          FADE IN
Later, Neyrelle awakens. Lorath and the Player are still asleep.
Lorath and the Player slowly get up.
